title: Burton Bags are Built for a Lifetime of Adventures
description:
The LIFETIME WARRANTY offered on all Burton bags and luggage is a reflection of the quality and durability that comes from 40 years of building and progressing our products. Go ahead and hit the road or trail with confidence knowing Burton bags are built to last.

Fall 2016 / Winter 2017 bags, packs and luggage out now.
